Hazard was <EVENT eid="e25" class="OCCURRENCE">named</EVENT> the PFA player of <TIMEX3 tid="t6" type="DURATION" value="P1Y">the year</TIMEX3> in <TIMEX3 tid="t7" type="DATE" value="2015">2015</TIMEX3> after he <EVENT eid="e26" class="OCCURRENCE">scored</EVENT> 14 times in 38 games to <EVENT eid="e27" class="OCCURRENCE">inspire</EVENT> Chelsea to the Premier League title. 
 
